    depends on SLE_TEAM_ST7789_ENABLE
    help
        Confirmed v4.4+ landscape 1.14 inch ST7789 module starts at row 53.
        Keep this paired with WIDTH=240, HEIGHT=135, X_OFFSET=40, MADCTL=0x60.

